587.name: Foot of the Volcano
desc: "   You have entered a clearing at the foot of the volcano. Standing
next to a lava tree you notice how the slight odor of sulphur poisons
the air. You hear the thunderous mumblings of the volcano as you notice
the tower of smoke escaping from its mouth. The black mountainside
twinkles in the sun from the peppered shards of obsidian. Through
the trees you see what might be a path up the mountain.
